// 褰撳墠瑙掕壊锛堥粯璁わ細瀹㈡湇鎬荤洃锛?let currentRole = "瀹㈡湇鎬荤洃";
let currentModule = "dashboard";
let currentHealthFilter = "all";

// 浠巐ocalStorage鍔犺浇鏉冮檺閰嶇疆锛堝鏋滄湁鐨勮瘽锛夊苟鑷姩杩佺Щ鏃ф牸寮?let rolePermissions = {};
(function initRolePermissions(){
  try {
    var saved = localStorage.getItem("chansee_permissions");
    rolePermissions = saved ? JSON.parse(saved) : {};
    // 杩佺Щ鏃ф牸寮忥紙string: "write"/"read"/"hidden"锛夆啋 鏂版牸寮忥紙object锛?    var needsMigration = false;
    var keys = Object.keys(rolePermissions);
    for(var k=0; k<keys.length; k++){
      var perms = rolePermissions[keys[k]];
      if(typeof perms !== 'object' || perms === null){ needsMigration=true; break; }
      // 妫€鏌ユ槸鍚︽湁妯″潡鏉冮檺浠嶆槸鏃ф牸寮?      var mks = Object.keys(perms);
      for(var m=0; m<mks.length; m++){
        if(typeof perms[mks[m]] === 'string'){ needsMigration=true; break; }
      }
      if(needsMigration) break;
    }
    // 濡傛灉娌℃湁鏁版嵁鎴栭渶瑕佽縼绉伙紝浣跨敤鏂扮殑榛樿閰嶇疆
    if(Object.keys(rolePermissions).length === 0 || needsMigration){
      var dp = (typeof DEFAULT_PERMISSIONS !== 'undefined' && DEFAULT_PERMISSIONS) ? DEFAULT_PERMISSIONS : {};
      rolePermissions = (dp && Object.keys(dp).length > 0) ? JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(dp)) : {};
      try { localStorage.setItem("chansee_permissions", JSON.stringify(rolePermissions)); } catch(e){}
    }
  } catch(e) {
    rolePermissions = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(DEFAULT_PERMISSIONS));
    try { localStorage.setItem("chansee_permissions", JSON.stringify(rolePermissions)); } catch(e2){}
  }
})();

// 淇濆瓨鏉冮檺閰嶇疆鍒發ocalStorage
function savePermissions() {
  localStorage.setItem("chansee_permissions", JSON.stringify(rolePermissions));
}

// 鑾峰彇褰撳墠瑙掕壊瀵规煇涓ā鍧楃殑鏉冮檺
function getPermission(module) {
  const rp = rolePermissions[currentRole];
  if (!rp) return { visible:false, view:false, edit:false, import:false, export:false, manage:false, scope:'all' };
  const mp = rp[module];
  // 鍏煎鏃ф牸寮忥紙string: "write"/"read"/"hidden"锛?  if (typeof mp === 'string') {
    if (mp === 'write') return { visible:true, view:true, edit:true, import:false, export:true, manage:false, scope:'all' };
    if (mp === 'read')  return { visible:true, view:true, edit:false, import:false, export:true, manage:false, scope:'all' };
    return { visible:false, view:false, edit:false, import:false, export:false, manage:false, scope:'all' };
  }
  // 鏂版牸寮忥紙object锛?  if (mp && typeof mp === 'object') return {
    visible: mp.visible!==false,
    view: mp.view!==false,
    edit: mp.edit===true,
    import: mp.import===true,
    export: mp.export===true,
    manage: mp.manage===true,
    scope: mp.scope || 'all'
  };
  return { visible:false, view:false, edit:false, import:false, export:false, manage:false, scope:'all' };
}

// 妫€鏌ュ綋鍓嶈鑹叉槸鍚﹀彲浠ョ紪杈戞煇涓ā鍧?function canEditModule(module) {
  return getPermission(module).edit === true;
}

// 妫€鏌ュ綋鍓嶈鑹叉槸鍚﹀彲浠ユ煡鐪嬫煇涓ā鍧?function canViewModule(module) {
  var p = getPermission(module);
  return p.visible === true && p.view === true;
}

